他從2012年開始[[太空自拍|太空自拍]]，有一些被張貼在[[Instagram|Instagram]]<ref>{{cite news |last=Gordon |first=Naomi |title=8 surprising celebrity selfies: Pope Francis, Darth Vader and the Obamas |url=http://www.digitalspy.com/celebrity/best-in-showbiz/a537500/8-surprising-celebrity-selfies-pope-francis-darth-vader-and-the-obamas.html |accessdate=December 27, 2013 |newspaper=Digital Spy |date=December 11, 2013 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131227155027/http://www.digitalspy.com/celebrity/best-in-showbiz/a537500/8-surprising-celebrity-selfies-pope-francis-darth-vader-and-the-obamas.html |archivedate=2013年12月27日 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，並位居2013年自拍列表的頂端<ref>{{cite news |title=Seven of the best selfies you will see today: As selfie is named word of the year, we round up seven of the best |url=http://metro.co.uk/2013/11/19/seven-of-the-best-selfies-you-will-see-today-as-selfie-is-named-word-of-the-year-we-round-up-seven-of-the-best-4192268/ |accessdate=December 27, 2013 |newspaper=Metro |date=November 19, 2013 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140330100222/http://metro.co.uk/2013/11/19/seven-of-the-best-selfies-you-will-see-today-as-selfie-is-named-word-of-the-year-we-round-up-seven-of-the-best-4192268/ |archivedate=2014年3月30日 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Obama caught snapping 'funeral selfie': Craziest selfies of all time |url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/best-selfies-time-gallery-1.1522211?pmSlide=1.1522187 |accessdate=December 27, 2013 |newspaper=NY Daily News |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131228093558/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/best-selfies-time-gallery-1.1522211?pmSlide=1.1522187 |archivedate=2013年12月28日 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

2014年6月10日，美國航空航天局宣布星出彰彥將負責指揮NEEMO 18海底探測任務前往[[水瓶座实验室|水瓶座实验室]]，任務開始於2014年7月21日，總共歷時9天<ref name="eighteen">{{cite web |url=http://www.nasa.gov/press/2014/june/nasa-announces-two-upcoming-undersea-missions/#.U6maKldj4jU |title=NASA Announces Two Upcoming Undersea Missions |date=June 10, 2014 |publisher=NASA |accessdate=June 26, 2014 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111231911/http://www.nasa.gov/press/2014/june/nasa-announces-two-upcoming-undersea-missions/#.U6maKldj4jU |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Bergin">{{cite web |url=http://www.nasaspaceflight.com/2014/06/neemo-returns-two-new-underwater-missions/ |title=NEEMO returns with two new underwater missions |last=Bergin |first=Chris |date=June 11, 2014 |publisher=[[NASAspaceflight.com|NASASpaceflight]] |accessdate=June 24, 2014 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111180205/https://www.nasaspaceflight.com/2014/06/neemo-returns-two-new-underwater-missions/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2021年4月23日參與[[SpaceX載人2號|SpaceX載人2號]]，他與美國太空人{{tsl|en|Shane Kimbrough|沙恩·金布羅}}、{{tsl|en|K. Megan McArthur|梅根·麥克阿瑟}}和法國太空人[[托马斯·佩斯凯|托马斯·佩斯凯]]一起發射升空。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nasa.gov/press-release/nasa-to-host-briefings-interviews-for-next-crew-rotation-mission-with-spacex|title=NASA to Host Briefings, Interviews for Next Crew Rotation Mission with SpaceX|accessdate=2021-04-24|archive-date=2021-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211208035944/https://www.nasa.gov/press-release/nasa-to-host-briefings-interviews-for-next-crew-rotation-mission-with-spacex/|dead-url=no}}</ref>4月24日，飞船与国际空间站对接。舱门打开后，他第一个进入国际空间站，与留在国际空间站的日本宇航员[[野口聪一|野口聪一]]重逢拥抱。这是自2010年野口和[[山崎直子|山崎直子]]后，11年来日本宇航员首次同时出现在国际空间站。

